metadata.name: Algorithmic Amour
metadata.description:
KEZIAI's first edition

Timed edition for Valentine's Day, 2023

Red Heart. Self-Love.  

Love is not just something to be sought after but something to be celebrated within yourself

Embrace your own unique algorithm of love and share it with the world

Open until 21st February  
You can mint as many as you'd like, they will be multiples of the same image, as it is an edition
